{"tid":1862020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣：針對中國來客全面封關 賀一誠：澳門不會封關","createTime":"2020-02-04T11:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T12:37:57.000Z","uid":120772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"797fa2537f321340429c3393ba50a5585005c140","tid":1862020,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>台灣</ins>針對中國來客全面封關 14 日內曾到大陸外籍人士禁入境</strong></span><br />\n自 2 月 7 日起，針對 14 日內曾經入境或居住於中國大陸的一般外籍人士，將禁止入境台灣，包括是享有免簽證待遇、落地簽證及電子簽證待遇及持有效簽證的外籍人士。<br />\n至於已持有居留證的外籍人士，若在 14 日內曾經入境或居住於中國大陸，於返台後將限制居住，並要自主健康管理 14 日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BE%86%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-14-%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A4%96%E7%B1%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C-14-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25B1%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=7fcb398a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C-14-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25B1%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%2F&h=976c2567\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BE%86%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-14-%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A4%96%E7%B1%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>澳門</ins>社會文化司︰政府暫時不考慮封關</span></strong><br />\n香港政府宣佈，午夜起關閉港澳碼頭、羅湖、落馬洲及皇崗 4 個口岸。被問到澳門會否跟隨封關？新型冠狀病毒感染應變協調中心副主席、澳門社會文化司司長歐陽瑜回應稱，澳門與香港情況不一樣，澳門有好多外僱及居民於珠海居住，<span style=\"color: red;\">而澳門居民有出入境自由，不可限制，政府暫時不會考慮關閉口岸。<br />\n呢啲時候就講自由</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%B8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258F%25B8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C%2F&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=88debe9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258F%25B8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C%2F&h=19025e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%B8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C/</a>"},{"pid":"d73fe6f72e8167e15d77cc8aabca2f46493178c1","tid":1862020